{{Flag entry|Image=Mao Zedong's proposal for the PRC flag.svg|Caption=草案一（黄河）}}
{{Flag entry|Image=Proposal 2 for the PRC flag.svg|Caption=草案二（黄河、长江）}}
{{Flag entry|Image=Proposal 3 for the PRC flag.svg|Caption=草案三（黄河、长江、珠江）}}
